PN,37101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777475480
OL,3,CHousehold waste size of a football
OL,4,Cpitch illegally dumped at protected
OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FAround 30,000 tonnes of household
OL,8,Fwaste the size of a football pitch has
OL,9,Fbeen dumped at a protected site in
OL,10,FLeicestershire.
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency urged the
OL,13,Fpublic to stay away from Cave's Inn
OL,14,FPits Site of Special Scientific
OL,15,FInterest, near the village of Shawell,
OL,16,Fwhile the "significant" amount of
OL,17,Fwaste is investigated.
OL,26,@xD@KOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
