OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777475480
OL,3,CHousehold waste size of a football
OL,4,Cpitch illegally dumped at protected
OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FThe area where the shredded household
OL,8,Fwaste has been dumped was "well-
OL,9,Fconcealed", according to the agency,
OL,10,Fand was only found after members of
OL,11,Fthe public reported a bad smell.
OL,13,FWhen Environment Agency and Natural
OL,14,FEngland officers visited the site,
OL,15,Fthey found layers of waste with soil
OL,16,Fused to cover it.
OL,18,FAlongside a criminal investigation,
OL,19,Fthe Agency said it is assessing local
OL,20,Fair and water quality to prevent any
OL,21,Ffurther environmental impact.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777475480
OL,3,CHousehold waste size of a football
OL,4,Cpitch illegally dumped at protected
OL,5,Csite
OL,7,F"A sickening case"
OL,9,FIan Jones, area director for the West
OL,10,FMidlands at the Environment Agency,
OL,11,Fsaid anyone with information about the
OL,12,Fillegal dumping should call their
OL,13,Fhotline.
OL,15,FHe said: "This is a sickening case of
OL,16,Flarge-scale illegal waste dumping, and
OL,17,Fwe share the public's disgust.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777475480
OL,3,CHousehold waste size of a football
OL,4,Cpitch illegally dumped at protected
OL,5,Csite
OL,7,F"We have launched an investigation
OL,8,Fwith Natural England to find the
OL,9,Fcriminals and ensure they pay the
OL,10,Fprice for their despicable actions.
OL,12,F"We ask the public to stay away from
OL,13,Fthe area, which is on private land,
OL,14,Fwhile we investigate."
OL,16,FAccording to Phil Hukin, principal
OL,17,Fmanager for Leicestershire and Rutland
OL,18,Fat Natural England, "the site
OL,19,Fcontained some of the best remaining
OL,20,Fareas of neutral marsh in
OL,21,FLeicestershire".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777475480
OL,3,CHousehold waste size of a football
OL,4,Cpitch illegally dumped at protected
OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FHe added: "It is heartbreaking to see
OL,8,Fone of England's precious Sites of
OL,9,FSpecial Scientific Interest damaged
OL,10,Flike this.
OL,12,F"Our officers are working closely with
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency colleagues to
OL,14,Finvestigate this appalling crime."
OL,16,FAnyone with information can report it
OL,17,Fto the Environment Agency incident
OL,18,Fhotline on 0800 80 70 60 or
OL,19,Fanonymously to Crimestoppers on 0800
OL,20,F555 111.
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUvD@bO]
